com.poesys.db.dao.query

Class QueryList<T extends IDbDto>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dao.query.QueryList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of IDbDto to query
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQueryList<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueryCacheList, QueryMemcachedList

    public class QueryList<T extends IDbDto>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IQueryList<T>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that queries a list of data transfer objects (DTOs) based on a SQL statement with no parameters. The list is guaranteed to be thread safe, and the DTOs should also be thread safe if you are going to use them in a multi-threaded environment.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
    See Also:
    IDbDto, IQuerySql
